ActAccessible Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of DIODORO (DINO) ZUPPA of Ottawa, Ontario, to act as Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Accessibility Standards Development Organization, to hold office during pleasure for a term of eighteen months or until such time as a new Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective October 30, 2024.
